%h2.project__heading MUSIC FROM OUTER SPACE MODULAR

%p.project__para My first forray into building modular synthesizers was with Music From Outer Space modules in 2015. I decided that I wanted to build in the Eurorack format, and designed panels fro three modules - the Voltage Controlled Oscillator, Voltage Controlled State Variable Filter and Voltage Controlled Low Frequency Oscillator.

